{"tid":46513,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[無法無天] 網上igshop既詐騙行為 請廣傳！","createTime":"2016-12-19T17:00:59.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-22T08:04:01.000Z","uid":67588,"like":62,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3b1d5bdb5561ee9e68bdd579ed198f032254cfaa","tid":46513,"uid":67588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T17:00:59.000Z","msg":"事到如今<br />\n經過左唔夠24小時之後<br />\n已經陸續有其他受害者<br />\n目前:<span style=\"font-size: large;\">3位受害者</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">此post目的在於希望比到其他受害人知道 請廣傳 如有其他人得知自己出事冇錢又冇貨 請馬上pm</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">各受害人已經報警 希望各位可以好心推一推<br />\n呢一單並非單一事件<br />\n店主有預謀咁食左受害人既錢<br />\n無法無天</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">店舖資料ig shop</span>: Keepersneaker (已改名)  <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jz9x15v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJz9x15v.jpg&h=0252c8bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現時為: Hongkongtgt<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/20/004639_a42e9b2bbbc4e4a508758cc601fd50e3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F20%2F004639_a42e9b2bbbc4e4a508758cc601fd50e3.jpg&h=256dbc0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後再改名為 igshop: love_life429<br />\n<br />\n最新資料(19/12/2016 11:45) :<span style=\"font-size: large;\">該igshop已將其帳戶删除</span><br />\n<br />\n該店係19/12/2016 晚上10時幾貼出最後一個po 但唔夠一小時後帳戶即被删除<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/028G007.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F028G007.jpg&h=bdd1fc10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n犯罪手法:<br />\n主要以因為計算價錢出錯為理由，向受害人表示要加錢，聲稱會退款但最終無疾而終<br />\n受害人無法聯絡店主 而受害人嘗試在貼文留言亦被删除以及封鎖帳戶<br />\n另外 即使受害人仍然要件貨 但去到依家已經無疾而終 錢貨兩樣都冇哂<br />\n<br />\n電話 (只有whatsapp) : <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">9558 5373<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n銀行戶口<br />\n滙豐銀行 124 411 836 838<br />\n恆生銀行 789 287 638 883<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cZ06MqJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcZ06MqJ.jpg&h=76e07d85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n受害人2號<br />\n<br />\n向店主訂購貨品<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/20/003728_62f5f6e72c29841ea584f675a73f09e5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F20%2F003728_62f5f6e72c29841ea584f675a73f09e5.jpg&h=5afa85e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n受害人揀岩貨品之後<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TsYF4rW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTsYF4rW.jpg&h=13a660eb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/20/003854_65bba4b19aa15ad04810578ad3e68a7d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F20%2F003854_65bba4b19aa15ad04810578ad3e68a7d.jpg&h=8341caf1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n店主有意引誘受害人買多幾件貨<br />\n佢可以食到既錢就越大<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/20/005130_12d31104c186e9218faaa3515242c1a0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F20%2F005130_12d31104c186e9218faaa3515242c1a0.jpg&h=be1b4983&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n透過銀行入數 匯款大約<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1900</span>比店主<br />\n<br />\n但當受害人再詢問貨品幾時有之際<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A8BDjgc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA8BDjgc.jpg&h=ce180093&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n店主已經第5日冇回覆受害人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n受害人第2位<br />\n<br />\n事主係Keepsneaker網店訂購左貨<br />\n<br />\nUltra Boost 3.0 Triple White<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o0j4pOd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo0j4pOd.jpg&h=719b39d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當時事主透過ATM機過數<br />\n手快冇拎到入數紙<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/72TiF36.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F72TiF36.jpg&h=2fde1a0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但透過銀行紀錄 已經同店主確認左入數<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/72TiF36.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F72TiF36.jpg&h=2fde1a0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n入數之後 店主表示貨品價錢有變動<br />\n詢問事主重要唔要對鞋<br />\n如果唔要 店主會退返錢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6aj4cwQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6aj4cwQ.jpg&h=b887e6c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事主想問下ultra boost uncaged價錢<br />\n但最後事主係第日決定退錢<br />\n而店主亦以okay回覆<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HPz858G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHPz858G.jpg&h=4a6b49e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但事後幾日 事主再查詢退款安排之際<br />\n店主亦沒有作出仼何回應<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事主嘗試打電話<br />\n但個號碼只係有whatsapp<br />\n並唔能夠打通<br />\n<br />\n事主之後係Keepsneaker ig貼文留言<br />\n但遭到店主删去留言並且即是封鎖用戶<br />\n<br />\n事主另外幾位幫手既朋友亦被封鎖抹去留言"},{"pid":"7a791a37aa5666476b306a015e26d5a8b76f970b","tid":46513,"uid":17817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T17:04:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b3f200d01918e72112333125a4f65c8548f2ea27","tid":46513,"uid":13474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T17:09:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0df09536079aa2607f2604570adfee0a8650b45b","tid":46513,"uid":1326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T17:09:35.000Z","msg":"正臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57d0da9529b6fb4965767ee09f22a3ab6e0735e6","tid":46513,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T17:10:02.000Z","msg":"報警未？"},{"pid":"0dbba25f811a8d1d5504492582671fe19eaf8d99","tid":46513,"uid":8719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T17:10:19.000Z","msg":"有戶口number 咪報警囉<br />\n之前有巴打比人呃左幾十蚊 條友都要坐監"},{"pid":"dfad857c24a2102463de2cf3e621948de6ec602a","tid":46513,"uid":21259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T17:10:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"688367dab7c099f3390ae66c360a37ce9a4d0f51","tid":46513,"uid":42622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T17:14:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0eea2ee551189748eee41206760b59a962425e26","tid":46513,"uid":24516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T17:16:25.000Z","msg":"推，條友垃圾到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好放過佢"},{"pid":"33e881d05431ec54b30f9c5337bcb2de5cad2882","tid":46513,"uid":42576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T17:23:28.000Z","msg":"屌你老母留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1df67ddcc07e23d3d98a50399858090e4f3d1f0b","tid":46513,"uid":67588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T17:33:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">重有一位受害人既資料未公佈 涉及金錢更超過4000蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小弟整理好就一次過貼出黎<br />\n<br />\n希望其他有買左野但重未知出事既人快啲聯絡我</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n請廣傳！"},{"pid":"176ee05bd2820c84048df24d1f5f2503e824717f","tid":46513,"uid":67588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T17:40:40.000Z","msg":"推呀推呀"},{"pid":"e8f0d047e0f2cc3a4a37cc8c3c17ff5d6ee8f17e","tid":46513,"uid":42350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T17:40:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 推"},{"pid":"6c0c48ac0abdba992aba2fe27fa029d25e1e1b4e","tid":46513,"uid":1239,"like":0,"dislike"